{"tid":1792142,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"高登仔一面倒批評連登既「和你影」藍絲攝影活動","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T23:54:27.000Z","uid":2889,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"35c8aee4973d9b72e85243c63ab88347efdea3bc","tid":1792142,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7159930/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7159930%2Fpage%2F1&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=4cd62ac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7159930/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n平時好少上高登 岩岩有朋友share高登呢個post 我一禁入去,嚇撚親,D留言完全一面倒同連登相反<br />\n我好撚好奇<br />\n點解兩個論壇網友既唸法可以完全唔一樣 究竟高登仔係咪同路人黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我有時都會睇下高登記者D直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />爆炸頭 軍火佬 崔銳蛋呢D 講野幾生動 <br />\n但唔係好明高登網友佢地唸乜?<br />\n其實好想知高登班網友有冇出過黎遊行/抗威?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe6d13a5416bbb8c5ab84dad6a87c7469e1a6c8","tid":1792142,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"大家星期六有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3KVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=ff2f4854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"5b3965f7b204f436e9f917779b792da33f129b29","tid":1792142,"uid":3115